window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Leviathan Fitness is known for monsters, muscles, and wolven who rescue damsels in distress.</p> <p>After a wedding cake catastrophe, local decorator Tegan finds herself being helped by a solid wall of fur and fangs named Atlas. She's never met anyone like him and finds herself enamored by his wolfish charm. After their sweet encounter, Atlas invites her to his gym anytime she needs his cake-lifting services.</p> <p>Tegan decides that instead—she wants to lift the cakes herself. She signs up for a membership with Leviathan Fitness, determined to build her strength.</p> <p>Primal desires emerge as Atlas and Tegan test just how much their new love can lift—and if there are any limits to what monsters and humans can do.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
